&lt;p&gt;This isn&#39;t API integration work. You&#39;ll define the patterns and systems that govern how AI reasons about and generates full-stack applications, driving initiatives that span multiple teams and influence our broader AI strategy. Your work shapes the experience of millions of users building real products with Bolt every day.&lt;/p&gt;
